Specifications
ASCO Red Hat general purpose 2-way normally closed solenoid valves will provide On/Off control of air, inert gas, water, light oil (300SSU) and other clean flowing media compatible with the materials of construction. This valve has one inlet and one outlet and does not pass fluid until the coil is energized. Used in a variety of applications including: automated systems, dispensing systems, welding equipment, restaurant equipment, food processing machinery, water treatment systems and laundry equipment.
Type: 2-Way Normally Closed (energize to open)
Pipe Size: 1-1/2" NPT, 1-1/4" Orifice, Cv 22.5

Coil Termination: 1/2" Conduit Hub with 18" lead wires
Agency Approvals: UL Listed, CSA certified, CE
Media Temperature: 180° F maximum
Ambient Temperature: 32-125° F nominal (minimum 0° F where freezing water is not a factor)
